title: Cafe Yumm
typeOfFood: Vegan-friendly, Lacto, Ovo, American, International, Organic, Fast food, Beer/Wine, Take-out, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. Chain of quick service restaurants in the Pacific Northwest, this one est. 2014. Offers bowls, sandwiches, salads, wraps, breakfast; has tempeh and tofu, vegan ginger cookies. Beverages are organic coffee, tea, local kombucha, and craft beer. Signature dish is the Yumm bowl which comes with choice of brown or jasmine rice, beans, and topped with sauce, salsa, veggies, and dairy - ask to make your bowl vegan, and kitchen will substitute cheese/cream for extra avocado or veggies. Has drive-thru. Some grab and go items.
